snippet.title: Stormy game night ! Elsa & Anna toddlers - family fun
snippet.description:
Shop for Disney products:  https://www.shopdisney.com/

Shop for Barbie / Mattel products:  https://barbie.mattel.com/shop#

In this toys dolls parody video little Anna and Elsa are preparing for a great family game night! They prepare snacks, while outside there is a rainstorm. What game will they play? Suddenly, the power goes out! All the lights are turned off. Will they be able to still continue the game ? Watch the video to find out, enjoy!
